CatalystX::StompSampleApps
a test app with bells & whistles

1) get the latest version of this package:
http://github.com/dakkar/CatalystX-StompSampleApps

2) install dependencies from http://github.com/dakkar/ :
Net::Stomp::Producer
Net::Stomp::MooseHelpers
CatalystX::ComponentsFromConfig
CatalystX::ConsumesJMS
Catalyst::ActionRole::JMS
Plack::Handler::Stomp

3) Commands:
deploy the database running app2_deploy.pl
    a file will be created: /tmp/events.db
run the app with app2.pl
send event with test_app2_sendevent.pl
tell the app to dump them with test_app2_dump.pl

